webpage.para:
    The Tracker products are a suite of information management tools and network service solutions for 
    Animal Agriculture producers, 
  	Infrastructure providers and Process control auditors. Tracker
  	product solutions are used to 



Document;



Manage;



Analyze;



Report;



Archive;



Query;



and Inter-exchange information between livestock business associates.

section.para:
  	Tracker Products:



Tracker Professional is a business intelligence toolkit
				for Data Acquisition, Analysis, Reporting and Integration;



Tracker Lite is an easy to use smart phone application for
				acquisition and retrieval of Livestock premises and animal information;



Tracker Cloud is a network service for archival, retrieval and query of livestock premises documents;



iRouter appliance is a configurable network event processor for the integration of sensors and actuators.
